---
import BaseLayout from '../../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const meta = {
  "title": "Penapis Udara CUCKOO K Model | Harga, Promo & Spesifikasi",
  "description": "Nikmati udara bersih dengan Penapis Udara CUCKOO K Model. Liputan luas 710 sqft, filter Ultra-Deo HEPA 13 & indikator 8 warna. Serendah RM89/bulan.",
  "canonical": "https://www.cuckoonano.com/products/air-purifier/k-model/",
  "ogImage": "https://www.cuckoonano.com/assets/images/products/air-purifier/k-model/k-model.webp",
  "ogType": "website"
};
---
<BaseLayout {...meta}>
  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <section class="hero-pattern px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand text-xs sm:text-sm">
          <span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-gold"></span> Penapis Udara
        </p>
        <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-black tracking-tight sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">K Model CUCKOO</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl font-bold text-brand-gold">Best Value • Ultra-Deo HEPA 13</p>
        <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-8 text-muted">
          Penapis udara dengan liputan luas 710 sqft pada harga mampu milik. Didatangkan dengan indikator kualiti udara 8-warna pintar dan rekaan yang mesra ruang.
        </p>
        
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white px-6 py-4 shadow-soft ring-1 ring-brand/10">
            <p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-brand">Pakej 5 Tahun</p>
            <div class="mt-1 flex items-baseline gap-1">
              <span class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tight text-brand">RM89</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-muted">/bulan</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
          <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=60139916967&text=Salam%20Fadhil,%20saya%20berminat%20dengan%20promo%20Penapis%20Udara%20K%20Model.%20Boleh%20bantu%20semak%20kelayakan?" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand px-8 py-4 text-center font-black text-white shadow-glow transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-brand-dark hover:shadow-xl">
            Semak Kelayakan
          </a>
          <a href="#features" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white px-8 py-4 text-center font-black text-brand ring-1 ring-brand/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-brand-soft">
            Lihat Spesifikasi
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-md lg:max-w-none">
        <div class="absolute -right-4 -top-4 z-10 rounded-full bg-brand-gold px-6 py-2 text-sm font-black text-white shadow-lg rotate-3">
          Coverage Besar
        </div>
        <div class="flex aspect-[4/5] items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-[2.5rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-brand-soft/40 p-8 shadow-2xl ring-1 ring-brand/10">
          <img src="/assets/images/products/air-purifier/k-model/k-model.webp" alt="Penapis Udara CUCKOO K Model" loading="eager" class="h-full w-full object-contain drop-shadow-xl transition-transform duration-700 hover:scale-105" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- KEY FEATURES -->
  <section id="features" class="bg-white px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="font-bold text-brand">Spesifikasi Pintar</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-black tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Kenapa Ramai Pilih K Model?</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-muted">K Model merupakan keseimbangan terbaik antara harga bajet dan prestasi tapisan yang bertaraf premium.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-[2rem] bg-cream p-8 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-brand-soft/50">
          <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand font-black text-white">1</div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-black">Liputan Luas (710 sqft)</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-muted">Mampu menyedut dan menapis udara kotor bagi ruang seluas pangsapuri studio atau ruang tamu rumah yang besar.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-[2rem] bg-cream p-8 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-brand-soft/50">
          <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand font-black text-white">2</div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-black">Ultra-Deo HEPA 13</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-muted">Didatangkan dengan sistem 7 lapisan tapisan bertaraf medikal yang memerangkap 99.97% habuk halus, PM2.5, hama, dan bau kepam.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-[2rem] bg-cream p-8 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-brand-soft/50">
          <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand font-black text-white">3</div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-black">Indikator 8-Warna</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-muted">Ketahui status kebersihan udara bilik menerusi paparan lampu LED dari warna Merah (paling kotor) hingga Biru (sangat bersih).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING PLAN -->
  <section class="bg-cream px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="rounded-[2rem] bg-white p-6 shadow-soft ring-1 ring-brand/5 sm:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-center text-brand">Harga & GOOODPLAN™</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-center text-muted">Sewa beli dengan servis percuma berkala yang diuruskan sepenuhnya oleh CUCKOO.</p>

        <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between rounded-2xl bg-brand-soft/20 p-6 ring-1 ring-brand/10">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-gold">Plan 5 Tahun</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-lg font-black text-brand">Pakej Mampu Milik (Syor Ejen)</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-bold text-muted">Tahun 1-3: RM94/bln <span class="mx-2 text-brand/30">|</span> Tahun 4-5: RM89/bln</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 sm:mt-0 text-right">
              <div class="flex items-baseline justify-end gap-1">
                <span class="text-4xl font-black text-brand">RM89</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-muted">/bln</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 rounded-2xl bg-cream p-6">
          <h4 class="font-black text-brand">Apa yang anda akan dapat?</h4>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm font-medium text-muted">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-brand font-bold">✓</span> Penghantaran dan pemasangan PERCUMA seluruh Malaysia.</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-brand font-bold">✓</span> Servis, cuci dan pensterilan produk setiap 4 bulan PERCUMA.</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-brand font-bold">✓</span> Pertukaran filter baharu secara berkala PERCUMA.</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-brand font-bold">✓</span> Waranti kerosakan alat ganti dan upah buruh PERCUMA selagi dalam kontrak.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="bg-white px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="font-bold text-brand">Sesuai Untuk Siapa?</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-black tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">FAQ CUCKOO K Model</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-cream p-6">
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg">Adakah K Model sesuai untuk pemilik kucing?</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-muted">Sangat sesuai! Dengan kemampuan menyedut yang sangat cekap dan filter Ultra-Deo HEPA 13, ia mampu menangkap bulu kucing yang berterbangan, mengurangkan risiko alahan, serta menghilangkan bau kepam najis kucing dengan cepat.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-cream p-6">
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg">Berapa kerap filter perlu ditukar?</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-muted">Anda tidak perlu risau tentang penukaran filter. CUCKOO akan menghantar ejen servis (Natural Care Service) ke rumah anda setiap 4 bulan untuk kerja-kerja mencuci, mensteril, dan menukar filter secara PERCUMA sepanjang tempoh kontrak.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-cream p-6">
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg">Bolehkah saya gunakan K Model di ruang tamu besar?</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-muted">Ya, dengan kapasiti liputan (coverage) sehingga 710 kaki persegi (710 sqft), prestasinya sangat berkuasa untuk meliputi ruang tamu bersaiz sederhana ke besar dengan mudah tanpa masalah.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DYNAMIC COMPONENTS -->
  <div data-promo></div>
  <div data-product-selector data-initial="air-purifier"></div>
  <div data-agent-block></div>
</BaseLayout>
